Variable Name  Long Name       SAS Type  Generic Type      Description
1  site_id     SITE_ID         8         NUMBER(4,0)       "Identification number or code for the site"
2  plot_id     PLOT_ID         $  8      NUMBER(3,0)       "The identification of the plot number within the site"
3  grid_id     GRID_ID         $  8      CHAR(5)           "Grid ID for sites collected in 1986 from  airphoto grid cell locations (see data file site_86.dat)"
4  latitude    LATITUDE        8         NUMBER(10,6)      "Latitude (decimal degrees), increasing to the north"
